# isaac sim安装(ubuntu20.04 3090)

下载地址https://docs.isaacsim.omniverse.nvidia.com/4.5.0/installation/download.html
下载isaac sim 4.5.0 linux(约7g)(对于50系显卡请安装isaac sim 5.0.0)

mkdir ~/isaacsim && cd isaacsim
将下载的isaacsim.zip 移动到~/isaacsim 并解压

./post_install.sh
./isaac-sim.selector.sh
直接点START
等待终端：[193.852s] Isaac Sim Full App is loaded.

添加环境变量
```
sudo gedit ~/.bashrc

在~/.bashrc中加入以下内容
# Isaac Sim root directory(Isaac_sim安装目录)
export ISAACSIM_PATH="${HOME}/isaacsim"
# Isaac Sim python executable
export ISAACSIM_PYTHON_EXE="${ISAACSIM_PATH}/python.sh"

```

检查模拟器能否运行：
```
${ISAACSIM_PATH}/isaac-sim.sh
```

检查模拟器是否能从独立的python脚本运行
```
# checks that python path is set correctly(output: Isaac Sim configuration is now complete.)
${ISAACSIM_PYTHON_EXE} -c "print('Isaac Sim configuration is now complete.')"
# checks that Isaac Sim can be launched from python
${ISAACSIM_PYTHON_EXE} ${ISAACSIM_PATH}/standalone_examples/api/isaacsim.core.api/add_cubes.py
```

# isaac lab安装

```
git clone https://github.com/isaac-sim/IsaacLab.git

cd Isaaclab

# create a symbolic link(请根据自己路径填写)
ln -s path_to_isaac_sim _isaac_sim 

./isaaclab.sh --conda unitree_sim_env
conda activate unitree_sim_env
./isaaclab.sh --install
```

测试是否安装成功
```
./isaaclab.sh -p scripts/tutorials/00_sim/create_empty.py
```
